    <div class="mt-10 prose prose-sm dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">About Our Free Online Tools</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">xConvert24 offers a growing library of over 30 free online tools designed for speed, simplicity, and privacy. Every tool on this page works instantly in your browser — there is no sign-up process, no account to create, and no usage limits to worry about. Whether you are a student calculating your BMI for a health class, a developer converting Unix timestamps, a musician tuning a guitar, or a traveller checking time zones before a meeting, we have a tool for you.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Why Choose xConvert24 Tools?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Most online tool sites bombard you with advertisements, pop-ups, and mandatory account creation before you can use anything. We take a different approach. Our tools load fast, work offline where possible, and respect your privacy. All calculations happen client-side in your browser — we never send your data to a server for processing. This means your passwords stay private, your financial calculations remain confidential, and your images never leave your device.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Built for Every Device</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Every tool in our collection is fully responsive and works beautifully on desktop, tablet, and mobile devices. The interfaces automatically adapt to your screen size, so you get the same powerful functionality whether you are at a desk or on the go. We test across Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and Edge to ensure consistent behaviour everywhere.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Categories at a Glance</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Our tools span several categories to cover the widest range of everyday needs. The <strong>Calculators</strong> section includes financial tools like loan and tip calculators alongside health tools like the BMI calculator and scientific tools for mathematical operations. The <strong>Time and Clocks</strong> section helps with scheduling across time zones, setting alarms, and measuring elapsed time. <strong>Creative and Media</strong> tools handle image editing, format conversion, and colour management without installing desktop software. The <strong>Security and Developer</strong> section includes password generation and network utilities. And our <strong>Finance and Crypto</strong> tools provide live market data at a glance.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Looking for Unit Converters?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">If you need to convert between units of measurement — weight, length, temperature, currency, speed, volume, pressure, and more — head over to our dedicated <a href="/convert" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline font-medium">Unit Converters</a> section. We have 25 specialised converters covering everything from Celsius to Fahrenheit to shoe sizes across international standards.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">New Tools Added Regularly</h3>
